narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Continued to build my skills as an accounting empirical researcher. Covered many pertinent topics to the field today, such as Earnings Management, Analysts, Valuation, Cost of Capital, and Regulation.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Alina is a great instructor. Her presentations at the start of each class really help to set the scene for the topics we will cover. She is also very good at connecting ideas across topics that we cover from week to week. The papers selected are of high quality, with many seminal works covered in the seminar.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Anyone interested in empirical capital markets research would benefit greatly from this class.
